"Overall:  Very nice and typical of the better versions of Black IPA.  Founders is living up to its reputation of producing enjoyable and solid brews.  It is very drinkable, well balanced and covers the alcohol content well with taste and feel.  Great beer for cold evenings!   Will certainly add this to my favorites list."
