"Dark Penance is something I could have before, during, or after a meal (depending on what's being served). Its combination of peach, caramel, coffee, and pine flavours affords it tremendous versatility. It's equally suitable as a little, late evening sip as it is a sociable, semi-sessionable quaffer. A more easy-going offering than it lets on, don't be at all afraid to pick up a full four pack."
