"O - Founders' Dark Penance has a wonderfully balanced aroma and flavor of dark malt and American piney hops, teetering between the two; it's in the feel where it's imbalance shines. Huge bitterness slays the tongue with gripping and sharp dryness that lingers for some time. Deceptively drinkable considering its hidden alcohol content, this imperial black IPA gets the job done well in every regard."
